item.title: Retrospective on my personality
item.description: Myer’s Briggs Mediator {INFP} Assertive Mediator (INFP-A) INFP As an INFP, I have found it difficult to get work which does not restrict my creative and intuitive style. I’m too idealistic and receive a lot of unwarranted criticism. This results in relationships and work being unfairly difficult for me to obtain. Case in point: Van Goh.
